title: Time Deposits, All Commercial Banks for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1914-1945 (2)--Original Data, 1947-1968. Source: Federal Reserve Board, Data For 1947-1960: Supplement To Banking And Monetary Statistics, Section 1 -- "Banks And The Monetary System", October 1962. Data For 1961-1968: Federal Reserve Bulletin, August 1967, Pp. 1307-1308 And Subsequent Issues (See Issue Of June 1968, P. A92 For Revision In Data).
